				"pudge_meat_hook"	"You can use Meat Hook after using Dismember if you have Blink Dagger to initiate. Otherwise, initiate Meat Hook first before using Dismember."
				"pudge_rot"	"Rot slows your foes and hurts them as well as yourself.

Does not disrupt any regeneration you\'re doing, so use Healing Salve or Bottle if you aren\'t taking any foreign damage."
				"pudge_flesh_heap"	"This ability is retroactive, so do not worry about getting this as soon as possible due to the number of kills you\'re racking up. Grab this after maximizing Hook."
				"pudge_dismember"	"There\'s a small delay on Dismember, so if Meat Hooking first, use Dismember immediately after (then Rot):

1. Meat Hook or Blink onto a target enemy
2. Use Dismember on them
3. Immediately use Rot if in-range
4. Follow-up with Meat Hook if unused
5. Continue Rotting if they haven\'t died yet"
